---
const year = new Date().getFullYear();
---
<footer class="relative mt-16 md:mt-24 border-t border-white/5">
  <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-5 md:px-8 py-14 md:py-20">
    <div class="grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-10">
      <div class="md:col-span-5">
        <a href="/" class="flex items-center gap-3">
          <span class="relative inline-block h-10 w-10 rounded-full overflow-hidden ring-1 ring-white/10">
            <img src="/logo.jpg" alt="Nova Nexus Texas logo" class="h-full w-full object-cover" width="40" height="40" />
          </span>
          <span class="font-display font-bold text-xl tracking-tight">
            <span class="nnt-gradient-text">Nova Nexus</span>
            <span class="text-white/80">Texas</span>
          </span>
        </a>
        <p class="mt-5 text-[color:var(--color-muted)] max-w-sm leading-relaxed">
          Transforming local businesses into standout brands — with confidence, clarity, and Texas-built grit.
        </p>
        <p class="mt-6 text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)]">Based in <span class="text-white">Arlington, Texas</span>. Serving the DFW Metroplex and beyond.</p>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-3">
        <h4 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[color:var(--color-muted)] mb-4">Explore</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5">
          <li><a class="hover:text-[color:var(--color-cyan)] transition" href="/">Home</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-[color:var(--color-cyan)] transition" href="/about">About</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-[color:var(--color-cyan)] transition" href="/services">Services</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-[color:var(--color-cyan)] transition" href="/pricing">Pricing</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-[color:var(--color-cyan)] transition" href="/gallery">Work & Wins</a></li>
          <li><a class="hover:text-[color:var(--color-cyan)] transition" href="/contact">Contact</a></li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <div class="md:col-span-4">
        <h4 class="text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.2em] text-[color:var(--color-muted)] mb-4">Get in touch</h4>
        <ul class="space-y-2.5">
          <li>
            <a class="hover:text-[color:var(--color-cyan)] transition" href="mailto:lupe@novanexustexas.com">
              lupe@novanexustexas.com
            </a>
          </li>
          <li class="text-[color:var(--color-muted)]">Arlington, TX · Central Time</li>
        </ul>
        <a href="/contact" class="nnt-btn nnt-btn-primary mt-6 !py-2.5 !px-5 text-sm">
          Book Free Discovery
          <svg xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" class="h-4 w-4"><line x1="5" y1="12" x2="19" y2="12"/><polyline points="12 5 19 12 12 19"/></svg>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="nnt-divider my-12"></div>

    <div class="flex flex-col md:flex-row items-center justify-between gap-4 text-sm text-[color:var(--color-muted)]">
      <p>© {year} Nova Nexus Texas. All rights reserved.</p>
      <p>Built in Texas · <span class="nnt-gradient-text font-semibold">AI-assisted, human-crafted</span></p>
    </div>
  </div>
</footer>
